es and sets.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \u201cIt is better than the world and everything in it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":14331,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1153 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/jihad-one-who-fights\/","url_meta":{"origin":14331,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Mujahid like one who constantly worships","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of one who strives in jihad in the way of Allah, and Allah knows best who strives in His way, is that of one who is always fasting and praying. Al